    <item>
      <title>新加坡银行在洗钱案后对富有客户展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/banks-scramble-to-close-loopholes-after-singapore-money-laundering-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，花旗集团、星展集团控股有限公司和其他卷入新加坡最大洗钱丑闻的银行正在加强对其富有客户和潜在客户的审查，以避免受到非法资金流动的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-09/banks-scramble-to-close-loopholes-after-singapore-money-laundering-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Jun 2024 23:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
